{"tid":1951688,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"孤高之人，日本雪山獨攀之行","createTime":"2020-03-31T06:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T04:33:12.000Z","uid":56817,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"90f69bbcaa81a5ae42baa0d0302d4f82efd5811d","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"在紀錄分享前，先「戴頭盔」，我是「獨攀」，基於香港有不少道德登山判官，審判「獨攀者」危害生命等話題，我只能說每位登山者都有自己選擇的攀登方式，旁外人不能用自己定義的風險去判斷。但前輩曾分享獨攀一詞是有一個更高的含意，並不只是獨自登山的意思。所以，這次登山定義是否「獨攀」，仍在腦裡交著。<br />\n<br />\n透過這次分享，希望更多登山人士能夠了解「獨攀」的真正含義。在初出茅廬時，有前輩說過「獨攀」不是指獨自登山，而是指在沒有安全防護下攀登會有嚴重下墮風險的山或岩壁，就是一個沒有失誤空間的世界，一失誤便回不了頭。「獨攀」是不能涉及固定繩的使用，不能是徒步型山峰，正如你不會跟人說我獨攀了麥理浩徑一樣。<br />\n<br />\n在世界上，總有一群執著定義，執著冒險。<br />\n**<br />\n在仆街中共和仆街港共玩死下，相信上年六月起，登山愛好者沒辦法及心情離開香港去登山，唯有藉此機會分享登山點滴。<br />\n**<br />\n想先行一步閱讀不同類型文章，可以點擊以下連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/unstoppabletraining/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funstoppabletraining%2F&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtAV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=1c301194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/unstoppabletraining/</a><br />\n<br />\n想看雪山相IG<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thin_air__\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fthin_air__&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtAV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=2175fad1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/thin_air__</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tLdPAwR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtLdPAwR.jpg&h=20191cbc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QgL6CLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgL6CLe.jpg&h=bcacdb74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4510e6e3edb980252cda327bb81512f2e4f5096","tid":1951688,"uid":193697,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:32:41.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c8fb1f26493c46371e508caddfc0cd374b1b04","tid":1951688,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"一定要留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7b164c2c032ac47988dee9348eead60c5f3eb8","tid":1951688,"uid":293864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:36:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"70c2cd8cb2298da6205bec5babf4fd7659744dcb","tid":1951688,"uid":271705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"有睇開你page,推!"},{"pid":"111aa709b0648235e54c0d837643d2237aba4e5e","tid":1951688,"uid":74486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬好有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b6e5f0987a1c09c447c259f7b926cd29344010","tid":1951688,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:41:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母好撚正"},{"pid":"4eb4bab87d6af2827361e9f0056385b9384c2cf6","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"近排流行行山抗疫，首先我諗唔明行山可以如何抗疫，笑話一則。<br />\n<br />\n而另一個笑話是不少香港行山專頁便食住潮流出來介紹抗疫路線，抗疫路線只得一條，就係留在家中。<br />\n<br />\n其中發現不少專頁都有比難度星星，但都是主觀評分，例如：釣魚翁郊遊徑是四星等，我頭都大埋，不明白究竟難度在哪，當然沒有錯的，只是香港沒有一套合用的等級標準，而我聯想到該專頁主理人體力一定很廢，其難度分析只是按體力分折。已阿爾卑斯攀登是有一套客觀標準，讓登山者可按客觀來選擇合適自己的路線。<br />\n<br />\n今日分享最簡單的Alpine Grade，讓大家看到有關阿爾卑斯式攀登的文章時能夠明白路線難度。<br />\n<br />\n▲ Alpine Grade （從低至高）<br />\n<br />\nF：路線當中涉及簡單的冰川行進，簡易的大石陣攀爬。可以幻想狗牙嶺和鹿巢石林加上冰川行進的攀爬。<br />\n<br />\nPD：路線當中涉及較複雜的冰川行進，地形會更陡削，需要基本的攀岩和冰攀技巧來攀登。<br />\n<br />\nAD： 路線當中涉及超過50度好雪坡，需要通過曝露感很強，會有下墜風險的路線，加上路線長度和複雜性增加，需要結繩同行。<br />\n<br />\nD： 路線當中涉及連續的岩攀，冰攀及雪坡攀登，其分段攀登難度比AD更難，加上地形複雜性，需配合更多綜合技術。<br />\n<br />\nTD：路線當中涉及部分攀登難度高的繩段，在一些很難到達的地方，攀登時間較長。有可能保護點放置難度高，安全性下降。<br />\n<br />\nED：最高我等級，大概就是高難度攀登，比TD的危險性更高，攀登時間可能需要數天。<br />\n<br />\nABO (Abominable) : 這是超越等級以外的評分，可以定義為分分秒秒也曝露在死亡威脅下，極難攀登的等級，大概就是噁心的路線。大部份的路線也不能夠重覆攀登。<br />\n<br />\n不要問我珠峰是什麼等級，如果是商業式攀登是不會在這個制度下評級。<br />\n可能有一點悶，不過是讓大眾明白，往後分享登山時，有一個客觀標準。減少到海外登山是選擇錯誤路線。<br />\n當中還有其他不同的等級來配合，而Alpine Grade是相對容易明白，每個Grade還有＋/- 來分級<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8cdjqn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8cdjqn.jpg&h=6b2149a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f9ee00e8077fc0c435c468309f3a9cbffc25d12","tid":1951688,"uid":274368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"呢D一定要留名<br />\n我都好想學攀山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7885da34ca6dfa5f872295137d1d8e86e388bae","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7e7ce0915c77d087ae9911ad966029f353848764","tid":1951688,"uid":74486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"好文要推"},{"pid":"80bdf4701eb723b734ee9eb6eed51f39f826f0aa","tid":1951688,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:10:44.000Z","msg":"好想去日本旅行，唔知幾時先可以lu"},{"pid":"31d69a4f357e0f18934a21cac72c8883b2c30d4c","tid":1951688,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"睇過孤高之人留名"},{"pid":"00652055cc251cfbbd7b4a9a1e63decb3b7e3488","tid":1951688,"uid":180572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4b65bb80058baf2e00bb8e9c7d544e7736154e62","tid":1951688,"uid":66200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"好耐之前已經follow緊樓主<br />\n留名睇分享"},{"pid":"5f0612938074dbe3bb806b0f7cbbf3c4b738b845","tid":1951688,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db490247b69ac9d9d06f8856b04ea826c481c549","tid":1951688,"uid":168389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:09:28.000Z","msg":"記得九月返香港投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa6c2d4f8032aab0785dcbba27ccc554fc04126","tid":1951688,"uid":265932,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T21:33:29.000Z","msg":"我份人好簡單 ，有山我就like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6a23f86a817b02564819262063ca7c5e2e2f40","tid":1951688,"uid":27652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T00:00:39.000Z","msg":"想學野lm"},{"pid":"7afb65413d9ec8a24c9f5613b06c3f183196e709","tid":1951688,"uid":8930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T00:24:57.000Z","msg":"留名學習"},{"pid":"7abb0620c571daac8064db43e7e7fa5706e63fb9","tid":1951688,"uid":130901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:56:50.000Z","msg":"香港班廢柴, 獨行香港山都批評危險, 食得屎啦<br />\n獨攀堅型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申, 只會獨行山"},{"pid":"e8e9096d528307a140367c94f9933143c469a58f","tid":1951688,"uid":322176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:41:16.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae68460793089e172dcf80b44bbe72a2e8be426","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"進山的第一天<br />\n<br />\n▲ 行程 ： 美濃户登山口 ► 赤岳礦泉<br />\n<br />\n早上在新宿車站乘坐JR中央線特急，約兩小時多便到達茅野站（Chino）。在特定日子，會有巴士接駁至美濃户登山口。可惜那天不是特定日子沒有公共巴士，卻有幸遇上日本登山者願意共乘的士至登山口，不但減省交通費，更協助很多言語上的難題。<br />\n<br />\n今天的目標是中午前到達赤岳礦泉，皆因我沒有入住酒店的關係，沒有寄存服務，所有行李也需要隨身約20公斤，是十分好的測驗，當然身體沒有讓我失望。由於，天氣和暖又有積雪，步道變得軟硬適中，行走時感覺為硬底的登山靴加上了緩震的鞋底一樣，爽耶 ~ 沿路也是上坡路沒有太多的冰面，所以不用加上冰爪。<br />\n<br />\n和日本登山者講太郎結伴而行，他適逢假日到山谷裡露營，所以行裝相對重。有同伴的時間十分快過，很快便到達分北沢和南沢的路口。因為我住在赤岳礦泉，所以往北沢的方向走，後段的路很美，被白雪所覆蓋的森林和河流，加上藍天的映照，很美。<br />\n<br />\n當走到大半時，同行的講太郎說步速太快了，很累。這是香港人的慣性，生活急促，但我的登山原則也是盡快脫離辛苦（重重的背包），再慢慢細嚐風景。當然，我沒有自己一個獨走，我讓他走在前方引領舒適的步速，而我在後方數十米慢慢地跟著。其實講太郎的步速一點也不慢～～～很累呀。當我到達赤岳礦泉時，他而為我跟赤岳礦泉的老闆安排好住宿，超級感動，旅途中巧遇不少日本人為我解決言語不通的問題。<br />\n<br />\n從美濃戶登山口至赤岳礦泉，約7.5公里路程，攀升750m，雪況正常的話是十分好走的路，我大概花了2.5小時左右便到達，據香港的師傅預計平常人負重慢走的路，約3 - 3.5小時應該也到能到達（時常被歸類不正常疾走者），是超級方便的山脈。全程也沒有追趕時間來行，用不氣喘不費勁的模式來完成，這一程的負重接近之旅證明訓練來得合適，針對性足夠。<br />\n<br />\n沒有花費體力來接近，讓我下午可以來一轉強度教大的暖身活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eU6J32R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeU6J32R.png&h=6f0b2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28eGQHX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28eGQHX.png&h=c53cb1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzRBEBo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzRBEBo.png&h=fdf235da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2LBFmPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2LBFmPM.jpg&h=3e47ffd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UxabtuS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUxabtuS.png&h=4e0cee1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNOsMgF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNOsMgF.png&h=a821c30b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/exZzrgM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FexZzrgM.png&h=724d2485&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AUu0mP8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAUu0mP8.jpg&h=094d1dbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ea468b0484162d90aece535b9c4ea2fee79f835","tid":1951688,"uid":122867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc516b0bbad78dae8f78d403a546583d62bc3fab","tid":1951688,"uid":121994,"like":0,"dislik