-03T10:45:32.000Z","msg":"好想學雪山登山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40eecc4989435b717ecf9b0283b30ba52fed52e","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f511d74b630175678dc88329508587f575830f","tid":1951688,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:45:32.000Z","msg":"好想學雪山登山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"可以留意我專頁"},{"pid":"2cf9bd62102cfb79555470e79613dfb850e93050","tid":1951688,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"唔好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3141980c5f0548735c649bfa48e30169478daf7","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cf9bd62102cfb79555470e79613dfb850e93050","tid":1951688,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"唔好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:01:10.000Z","msg":"點都留命睇支爆"},{"pid":"c7888596b21af061dde17712adb708fbfc12a2f1","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"►「 UIAA III+ 305m 3-4 hours  AD- 1   ▌ ▲  」<br />\n<br />\n▲ 行程 ：  赤岳礦泉 ► 阿弥陀岳 北稜 ► 赤岳礦泉<br />\n<br />\n日本技術路線的分級制有一點模糊，但完成了最低級數便了解和國際等級的對照。 阿弥陀岳北稜屬於技術路線，當中兩個岩壁位置約是法制的45米3級和40米2級，在網絡上找到結繩攀登的登山者共分4個繩段作攀登，實地考量後，個人認為2-3繩段便可以。在紀錄分享前，先「戴頭盔」，我是「獨攀」完成此路線，基於香港有不少道德登山判官，審判「獨攀者」危害生命等話題，我只能說每位登山者都有自己選擇的攀登方式，旁外人不能用自己定義的風險去判斷。但前輩曾分享獨攀一詞是有一個更高的含意，並不只是獨自登山的意思。所以，這次登山定義是否「獨攀」，仍在腦裡交著。<br />\n<br />\n****以下所寫的時間，請自行增加30%，我腳步偏快。 <br />\n<br />\n早上吃燒魚早餐後，收拾行裝後便踏上阿弥陀岳北稜探索的路途上，在接近技術路線前也使用我最愛的Gipron登山杖，攀登技術路線平常會使用單枝登山杖作平衡及上坡省力所用。約25分鐘到達行者小屋，沿著文三郎步道走，當看到阿弥陀岳便轉進去，在途中會發現進入林道的路徑。這就是上攀至北稜的林線，當天天氣不好，整天也在霧裡攀登，在連接北稜的陡坡前，把登山杖換上冰斧，Climb on !<br />\n<br />\n由於網絡上很多影片也有記錄，所以路況也有印象，直到一個約50-60度的雪坡，從揸著斧身上爬，變成握著斧柄一步一步踏實地上攀。終於看到第一岩壁，整個岩壁約40米，但攀登困難段只有5-7米，是法制等級3左右，我在這裡猶豫左一會，因為穿著手套沒有漂亮把手，又害怕失手滑倒便下墮，這就是菜鳥的不安和矛盾，最後原來不少隱藏了的冰面可用，突破了第一難關後便看到第二岩壁，看像很高的岩壁，但因為不是直壁和無限把手，沒有什麼猶疑便通過了，大概是法制等級2。 接著第二岩壁的是傳說之中的瘦稜（Thin ridge)，基於天氣不好，沒什麼曝露感可言，加上我經歷過阿爾卑斯的瘦稜縱走，所以一切盡在掌握之中。<br />\n<br />\n經過最後一百米的雪坡後，便到達阿弥陀岳的佛像即是山頂，以1小時54分完成我人生第一條的獨攀路線。轟轟作響的風來慶祝我登頂，在自拍時有日本登山者從中岳沢上來，他為拍了張登頂紀念。<br />\n然後，我便收起冰斧，拿出我心愛的登山杖向赤岳方向走。<br />\n<br />\n▲攀登後感<br />\n<br />\n登山最困難的是找能力相若同伴，想脫離菜鳥的我，沒辦法跟上難度攀登，又沒有帶新手的能力，在苦悶的香港只想離開去登山，想過師傳的介紹和網上的資料便決定到日本攀登這條路線。完成後好像成就解鎖一樣，有時獨話，有時結伴也有不同的感受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在此說句不好意思，因為太專注在攀登上，完成沒有拍過路線的照片，Gopro的影片也十分凌亂，只有我的雙斧，不好看呢。 <br />\n<br />\n     <br />\n ▌ 我愛的是登山，不是裝帥，但因為沒有帥氣照片，也會傷心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmxQMEc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmxQMEc.jpg&h=e3280f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiucfxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjiucfxA.jpg&h=8558e088&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fm66jZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm66jZn.png&h=caf03d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4sJcZZo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4sJcZZo.jpg&h=b319afeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGur4q4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGur4q4.jpg&h=fee31104&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4189c1ac81918bbec4c89ecf77f7e8575d59e879","tid":1951688,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:51:56.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f06f2055a4b007348138b035adb02b51229e0e0b","tid":1951688,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T20:08:17.000Z","msg":"LM 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c40050010e8f9e8619f5dc72a9dd6786fa1e3f","tid":1951688,"uid":67391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T20:13:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"43e73c0ee180d12da1bf885bed32c9ca885501fc","tid":1951688,"uid":6145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T20:16:23.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"fb9830bc104780430031a7b78f9f030fc0c052ae","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T01:33:52.000Z","msg":"【八ヶ岳】漏斗溪第二瀑 - ジョウゴ沢 F2  ▲ <br />\n<br />\n►「 緊張情緒讓肌肉加快崩緊   ▌ ▲  」<br />\n<br />\n▲ 行程 ： 赤岳礦泉► 某漏斗溪第二瀑 - ジョウゴ沢 F2. 15米<br />\n<br />\n在赤岳礦泉放下背包後，極速換上攀登的技術裝備，來一個快的午餐後，便走進山屋前的森林小徑。數分鐘後便到達大同心沢的路口，帶著無比興奮的探索心情不斷往上走，登山旅途上，探索未知領域是最讓我喜悅的事，那一種不安感和新鮮感使你的腎上腺素不斷上升。那天下午的溫度略高，大同心沢兩旁的雪坡呼出雪崩的感覺，直至看到曾發生輕微雪崩的痕跡後，決定快速看看大同心冰瀑便下撤。 看過第一段冰瀑後 ，只有三十米半繩的我便決定回頭了，上攀後需花功夫才能下降，除了懶惰外更是菜烏的不安呼喚我回頭是岸，用半跑半行的方式，很快便回到大同心沢的路口。<br />\n<br />\n我繼續往裹同心沢的方向探索，在第二個路口再次憑直覺轉入小徑，不出所料很快便遇到簡短的冰瀑作為熱身，當時已是三點半，所以巧遇一群完成攀冰訓練的大學生正在下撤。到達一幅15米的冰瀑前，考慮了兩秒便決定上攀，粗略估計是WI 3 的難度，是有信心獨攀。由於，久沒攀冰及沒有防護的狀態下，恐懼使我呼吸節奏錯亂，手也有點疲累，當然沒有回頭的空間，也硬著頭皮完成短短的冰瀑。在冰瀑頂上遇日本年輕的登山嚮導大輔，懶惰的我便借他的繩子沿繩下降回到起攀點。幸好遇到大輔，我的繩子應該不足夠下降距離，若自行設置又花功夫了。  <br />\n<br />\n和大輔結伴下撤回赤岳礦泉，他獨攀了河谷裡的冰瀑作訓練，然後即日回到家中。很羨慕他們可以有如此方便的訓練場所。不禁也讓我想起住在霞慕尼90天的計劃，可惜登山同伴難求。大輔給我聯絡方法，下回登山可以找他結伴登山。<br />\n<br />\n回到赤岳礦泉後，梳洗完便可享用晚餐，無啤酒不歡的我，看到啤酒櫃眼睛閃閃發光，登山配上啤酒是最幸福的事。<br />\n     <br />\n ▌ 獨攀的最大難題是面對恐懼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezgKaj9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezgKaj9.jpg&h=19227830&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4w5yN6R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4w5yN6R.jpg&h=e3fd5239&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oW195Tx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoW195Tx.jpg&h=f97462ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMQ3qTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMQ3qTy.jpg&h=afed277e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMGaQke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMGaQke.jpg&h=e5f717df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fnePmrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfnePmrV.jpg&h=74fefe47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDmumrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDmumrX.jpg&h=fb83c6cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpcpUMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpcpUMY.jpg&h=199e2e62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9dd47b4f7fbab4a6bdd35971878c7b22c0cecaa","tid":1951688,"uid":262575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:21:34.000Z","msg":"唔撞期的話，都有興趣報班<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報班冇要求唔怕嗎？"},{"pid":"f11b0fcbec533948dc36e7045e8e1c6ec2958ca5","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"►「  日本山屋奇遇 ▌ ▲ 」<br />\n<br />\n近日，香港瘋狂討論一窩蜂擁入山區，遺下大量垃圾。在山上應有的品格，也是教育出來，通山垃圾其實並不是今天才出現，閒時也發現不少紙巾和膠樽。如今大量垃圾出現，是因為一窩蜂出現的人群所致。這是最漫長的教育問題，但總有腐敗。<br />\n<br />\n而我在日本赤岳砿泉住了兩個晚上，服務十分完善。但是在第二晚後，早上醒來我的一雙冰斧不翼而飛，應該被山中小偷看中了，最終未能尋回。<br />\n<br />\n你可能會說是我沒有好好看管裝備，但其實大部山屋也規定不能把裝備帶到睡覺的房間，要放在房外。而赤岳砿泉更需要把所有行裝放在房外，所以遇上品格不好的登山人士是我不幸，其後巔佬表示，這不是首次聽見。縱使在意大利和法國以小偷聞名的國家，在山屋所有裝備也要放在裝備室也從沒有出意外，但卻發生在以品行端正的日本，獲得此經驗。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我一肚傷心的怒氣，拿著兩枝登山杖，來一趟極速縱走，然後直接衝回市區，沒有了一對冰斧等於沒有了手把，更沒有了登山之情緒。<br />\n<br />\n各位，入住山屋也要小心行裝，再好教育的國家也有少量壞掉的人。<br />\n<br />\n▌R.I.P. 我的一天戰友。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqZ7VzA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqZ7VzA.jpg&h=ba3de6c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d9e240040a7e50eddcc71e19e666e5ed44416b7","tid":1951688,"uid":41796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b40eecc4989435b717ecf9b0283b30ba52fed52e","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f511d74b630175678dc88329508587f575830f","tid":1951688,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:45:32.000Z","msg":"好想學雪山登山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"可以留意我專頁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"留名學野，想學冰攀"},{"pid":"0eb7d2d93c618f8cc2e66ab96a57fa05a67ee386","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T00:30:21.000Z","msg":"堆！"},{"pid":"cf045b7b7e8b737db3925aa6533dbd7cc996ffff","tid":1951688,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"巴打有無睇眾神的山嶺"},{"pid":"ec6f4d47e4dde4e4948db364964d20d2b2b20eb2","tid":1951688,"uid":120229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cd03dfa6fb83f740f8feb0c7dbf352d6d07570a","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5807e1b20f28d58d0cebddf3871f8513b9c7a93d","tid":1951688,"uid":120229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:42:41.000Z","msg":"想知你英文名係咪h字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:01:00.000Z","msg":"🤣🤣🤣🤣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"Asso同學～"},{"pid":"beec1faa166fef3c9758a25516a729556fd4d5d0","tid":1951688,"uid":265932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0eb7d2d93c618f8cc2e66ab96a57fa05a67ee386","tid":1951688,"uid":56817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T00:30:21.000Z","msg":"堆！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"入唔入group?"}]}